om: 1; margin-top: 0px !important; line-height: 1.15 !important;\">Ayanâ€™s Academy: Your personal path to success.</b></p></div>', '2026-03-29 06:45:58');
INSERT INTO `pte_courses_campus` (`id`, `course_title`, `course_image`, `course_short_description`, `lecture_hour_details`, `course_amount`, `course_level`, `total_lecture`, `how_many_hour_lecture`, `course_long_description`, `course_curriculum`, `created_at`) VALUES
(7, 'PTE 1 to 1 Long Course', 'uploads/pte-courses-campus/1775965394_4959_e7600ab79078a17f6f62906d9db34d3a.jpg', '## **PTE 1-to-1 Long Course | Ayanâ€™s Academy**\r\n\r\nExperience the ultimate in personalized coaching with our **22-class** premium program. This course is built for students who demand undivided attention and a 100% customized roadmap to a **79+ score**.\r\n\r\n* **Total Classes:** 22 Private 1-to-1 Sessions.\r\n* **Unique Service: AI Voice & Logic Sync.** Your trainer performs a deep-dive analysis of your \"Acoustic Footprint\" to ensure your speaking perfectly triggers the Pearson AI algorithm.\r\n* **Extensive Focus:** Zero generalized teaching. Every minute is spent fixing *your* specific weaknesses in high-value tasks like **Read Aloud** and **Write From Dictation**.\r\n* **Certified Excellence:** Direct mentorship from **Pearson-certified trainers** who provide real-time corrections.\r\n* **Flexible Learning:** Study at your own pace, either **On-Campus** or **Live Online**.\r\n\r\n**Maximum focus. Zero distractions. One target score.**\r\n\r\n---\r\nðŸ“ž **Enroll Now:** 01319904015\r\nðŸ“ **Ayanâ€™s Academy: Your personal path to success.**', '44', 25000.00, 'Advanced', 22, '2', '<h2 data-path-to-node=\"0\">Master Your Craft: The Definitive Learning Experience at Ayanâ€™s Academy</h2><p data-path-to-node=\"1\">In an era of endless tutorials and superficial workshops, <b data-path-to-node=\"1\" data-index-in-node=\"58\">Ayanâ€™s Academy</b> stands as a beacon for those who demand depth, rigor, and professional legitimacy. Our flagship program is not just a courseâ€”it is a strategic investment in your future, built on the pillars of international standards and intensive, focused training.</p><p data-path-to-node=\"2\">At Ayanâ€™s Academy, we believe that mastery isn\'t found in how long you sit in a classroom, but in the <b data-path-to-node=\"2\" data-index-in-node=\"102\">quality of the guidance</b> and the <b data-path-to-node=\"2\" data-index-in-node=\"134\">intensity of the focus</b>.</p><hr data-path-to-node=\"3\"><h3 data-path-to-node=\"4\">The Power of Pearson-Certified Mentorship</h3><p data-path-to-node=\"5\">The true value of an education lies in the expertise of the educator. Our trainers are <b data-path-to-node=\"5\" data-index-in-node=\"87\">Pearson-certified</b>, meaning they have met the rigorous global benchmarks set by one of the worldâ€™s leading learning companies.</p><ul data-path-to-node=\"6\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"6,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"6,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Global Standards:</b> You aren\'t just learning local \"best practices\"; you are being trained according to international professional requirements.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"6,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"6,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Expert Insight:</b> Our trainers bring a wealth of practical knowledge, moving beyond the textbook to show you how concepts are applied in high-stakes environments.</p></li></ul><h3 data-path-to-node=\"7\">22 Classes of Radical Focus</h3><p data-path-to-node=\"8\">We have stripped away the filler to create a <b data-path-to-node=\"8\" data-index-in-node=\"45\">22-class intensive curriculum</b>. While other programs may drag on for months, we maximize every minute. This \"extensive focus\" model is designed for high-achievers who want to reach professional proficiency quickly without sacrificing the depth of their understanding.</p><p data-path-to-node=\"9\"><b data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Our Curriculum Highlights:</b></p><ol start=\"1\" data-path-to-node=\"10\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"10,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"10,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Deep-Dive Modules:</b> Each session is dedicated to a core pillar of the subject matter, ensuring no stone is left unturned.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"10,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"10,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Accelerated Logic:</b> We use a structured pedagogical approach that builds your skills layer by layer, turning complex theories into second nature.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"10,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"10,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Active Engagement:</b> Small class settings allow for direct interaction with our Pearson-certified staff, ensuring your specific questions never go unanswered.</p></li></ol><hr data-path-to-node=\"11\"><h3 data-path-to-node=\"12\">Why Ayanâ€™s Academy is Different</h3><p data-path-to-node=\"1\">In a crowded educational landscape, <b data-path-to-node=\"1\" data-index-in-node=\"36\">Ayanâ€™s Academy</b> distinguishes itself by moving away from the \"one-size-fits-all\" approach. We bridge the gap between academic theory and professional mastery through three core pillars:</p><ul data-path-to-node=\"4\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"4,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"4,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Modern Pedagogy:</b> Our trainers don\'t just know the subject; they are certified in the most effective ways to <i data-path-to-node=\"4,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"108\">teach</i> it, ensuring you retain more in less time.</p></li></ul><h3 data-path-to-node=\"5\">2. Radical \"Extensive Focus\"</h3><p data-path-to-node=\"6\">We believe that breadth without depth is a disservice to the student. Our curriculum is characterized by <b data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"105\">Extensive Focus</b>, meaning we prioritize the \"hard\" skills that others often gloss over.</p><ul data-path-to-node=\"7\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"7,0,0\">We dive deep into the complexities of the industry.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"7,1,0\">We prioritize mastery over simple familiarity.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"7,2,0\">Every module is designed to challenge you, pushing you beyond surface-level understanding.</p></li></ul><h3 data-path-to-node=\"8\">3. The 22-Class High-Impact Blueprint</h3><p data-path-to-node=\"9\">Efficiency is our signature. We have distilled a comprehensive body of knowledge into exactly <b data-path-to-node=\"9\" data-index-in-node=\"94\">22 classes</b>.</p><ul data-path-to-node=\"10\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"10,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"10,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">No Filler:</b> Every session is calculated to provide maximum value, eliminating the \"fluff\" found in longer, drawn-out programs.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"10,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"10,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Structured Progression:</b> This isn\'t a collection of random lectures; it is a meticulously planned 22-step journey from foundational knowledge to professional expertise.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"10,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"10,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Commitment to Completion:</b> Our format is designed for the serious learner who wants a clear start, a clear end, and a definite transformation in between.</p></li></ul><hr data-path-to-node=\"14\"><h3 data-path-to-node=\"15\">Your Journey to Excellence Starts Here</h3><p data-path-to-node=\"16\">Whether you are looking to pivot your career, upgrade your current skillset, or gain a competitive edge in the market, Ayanâ€™s Academy provides the environment you need to succeed. We don\'t just provide a certificate; we provide the <b data-path-to-node=\"16\" data-index-in-node=\"232\">confidence</b> that comes from being trained by the best.</p><p data-path-to-node=\"17\"><b data-path-to-node=\"17\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Are you ready to commit to your growth? Join Ayan\'s Academy and experience the difference that elite certification and intensive focus can make.</b></p><hr data-path-to-node=\"18\"><p data-path-to-node=\"19\"><b data-path-to-node=\"19\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Enrollment is now open. Space is limited to maintain our signature focus.</b></p>', '<div _ngcontent-ng-c1840272799=\"\" inline-copy-host=\"\" class=\"markdown markdown-main-panel enable-updated-hr-color\" id=\"model-response-message-contentr_092b714a99da6743\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-busy=\