(6, 'PTE Long Course 1 to 1', 'uploads/pte-courses-online/1775893219_1404_e7600ab79078a17f6f62906d9db34d3a.jpg', '## **PTE Online Long Course (1-to-1) | Ayanâ€™s Academy**\r\n\r\nAchieve your **79+ target** from home with our most comprehensive private program. This **22-class** digital bootcamp offers 100% undivided attention and expert screen-sharing guidance.\r\n\r\n* **Total Classes:** 22 Private Live Sessions.\r\n* **Unique Service:** **Remote AI Calibration.** We use specialized software to analyze your microphone quality and vocal frequency, ensuring the Pearson AI captures your fluency perfectly online.\r\n* **Extensive Focus:** Deep-dive drills into high-weightage tasks (*Read Aloud*, *Write From Dictation*) with real-time screen corrections.\r\n* **Expert Mentors:** 1-to-1 coaching with **Pearson-certified trainers** via Zoom/Google Meet.\r\n* **Digital Lab:** Full access to our premium online practice platform with real-exam questions.\r\n\r\n**Your personal classroom. Your target score. Any location.**\r\n\r\n---\r\nðŸ“ž **Enroll:** 01319904015\r\nðŸ“ **Ayanâ€™s Academy: Global Success, Personalized.**', '44', 20000.00, 'Advanced', 22, '2', '<div _ngcontent-ng-c2439404967=\"\" inline-copy-host=\"\" class=\"markdown markdown-main-panel enable-updated-hr-color\" id=\"model-response-message-contentr_b0bfd2804f165638\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-busy=\"false\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: linear; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none; appearance: none; background: none 0% 0% / auto repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border: 0px rgb(31, 31, 31); inset: auto; clear: none; clip: auto; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); columns: auto; contain: none; container: none; content: normal; cursor: auto; cx: 0px; cy: 0px; d: none; direction: ltr; fill: rgb(0, 0, 0); filter: none; flex: 0 1 auto; float: none; gap: normal; hyphens: manual; interactivity: auto; isolation: auto; margin-right: 0px; margin-b